snippet.title: Funky Funions!
snippet.description: Funky Funions! is a video game playing entrepreneur. This isn't a personal project, it's more of an individual venture that yields no monetary returns. I get the sweet satisfaction of dopamine from every like, every view, every subscribe, every comment. Funky Funions! is also known for his no-nonsense attitude and killer sense of humor. Funky Funions! can spend 48 hours telling jokes and you'll probably find at least one of them to be somewhat entertaining. That's how awesomely epic Funky Funions! is. If you see Funky Funions! in public, DO NOT ask for an autograph. Funky Funions! is too busy being epic to sign things.
